{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-228-minkowski-sums","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 228: Minkovski zbir","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Neka je $S_n$ regularan poligona sa $n$ stranica – ili oblik – koji ima vrhove $v_k (k = 1, 2, \\ldots, n)$ sa koordinatama:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; x_k = cos(\\frac{2k - 1}{n} × 180°) \\\\\n&#x26; y_k = sin(\\frac{2k - 1}{n} × 180°)\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Svaki $S_n$ je definisan kao popunjena figura koja uključuje sve tačke na granici i unutar nje.</p>\n<p>Minkovski zbir (ili Minkowski suma), $S + T$, dva skupa $S$ i $T$ je rezultat sabiranja svake tačke u $S$ sa svakom tačkom u $T$, gde se sabiranje tačaka vrši koordinatno: $(u, v) + (x, y) = (u + x, v + y)$.</p>\n<p>Na primer, zbir $S_3$ i $S_4$ je šestostrani oblik prikazan u ružičastoj boji dole:</p>\n<img alt=\"image showing S_3, S_4 and S_3 + S_4\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/minkowski-sums.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Da li $S_{1864} + S_{1865} + \\ldots + S_{1909}$ ima koliko delova?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4511000cf542c50ff63","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301871,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-228-minkowski-sums"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function minkowskiSums() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nminkowskiSums();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>minkowskiSums()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>86226</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(minkowskiSums(), 86226);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-228-minkowski-sums","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-229-four-representations-using-squares","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-227-the-chase","id":"5900f4511000cf542c50ff63","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-228-minkowski-sums"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}